#: ../../../docs/middlewares/authenticate.rst:2
msgid "Authenticate"
msgstr "Authentification"

#: ../../../docs/middlewares/authenticate.rst:4
msgid ""
"The ``authenticate`` middleware allow one to perform HTTP basic and digest "
"authentication."
msgstr ""
"Le middleware ``authenticate`` permet d'effectuer une authentification de "
"base ou haché."

#: ../../../docs/middlewares/authenticate.rst:7
msgid "It takes three parameters:"
msgstr "Il prend trois paramètres:"

#: ../../../docs/middlewares/authenticate.rst:9
msgid "an ``Authentication`` object described in :doc:`../vsgi/authentication`"
msgstr ""
"un objet de type ``Authentication`` décrit dans :doc:`../vsgi/authentication`"

#: ../../../docs/middlewares/authenticate.rst:10
msgid "a callback to challenge a user-provided ``Authorization`` header"
msgstr ""
"une fonction de rappel pour mettre à l'épreuve une en-tête ``Authorization`` "
"fournie par l'agent utilisateur"

#: ../../../docs/middlewares/authenticate.rst:11
msgid ""
"a forward callback invoked on success with the corresponding authorization "
"object"
msgstr ""
"une fonction de rappel invoquée en case de succès avec l'objet "
"d'autorisation correspondant"

#: ../../../docs/middlewares/authenticate.rst:14
msgid ""
"If the authentication fails, a ``401 Unauthorized`` status is raised with a "
"``WWW-Authenticate`` header."
msgstr ""
"Si l'authentification échoue, une erreur ``401 Unauthorized`` sera lancée "
"avec pour message le contenu de l'en-tête ``WWW-Authenticate``."

#: ../../../docs/middlewares/authenticate.rst:25
msgid ""
"To perform custom password comparison, it is best to cast the "
"``authorization`` parameter and access the password directly."
msgstr ""
